QuestData.Title: Find Acteon!
QuestData.Description: You did a wonderful job, $n. Our people will be thankful for this bounty. With that said, would you mind taking this haul of red snapper to Acteon at Azure Watch?$B$BHe shouldn't be hard to find as he is awaiting this catch.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Crate of Red Snapper to Acteon at Azure Watch.
QuestData.CompletionText: What do you think of my armor? Crafted it myself! It's a little different than what we'd traditionally wear but extremely comfortable.
QuestData.RewardText: Poor Diktynna... That murloc gave her quite a scare.$B$B<Acteon sighs.>$B$BHopefully she will recover from the injuries soon...$B$BSo I presume you're looking for work. Well there's plenty of that to be found at Azure Watch!
